WEBVTT

00:00.001 --> 00:03.289
Subtitles by explosiveskull

00:09.609 --> 00:12.044
Ben, that's too heavy for you.
Just wait for your dad.

00:12.711 --> 00:14.244
CASSIE: Okay, just put it
by the table.

00:14.246 --> 00:15.347
ASHLEY: I wanna see it.

00:17.250 --> 00:19.518
- Or just drop it right there.
- Ashley!

00:20.685 --> 00:24.655
It's okay, sweetie. We just have
to put it back in

00:24.657 --> 00:27.758
because if Santa steps on one
of these ornaments he might just

00:27.760 --> 00:29.659
- drop off your gifts next door.
- [BALLS TUMBLING]

00:29.661 --> 00:30.596
[GASPS]

00:31.562 --> 00:33.332
- I'm kidding.
- [BOTH LAUGHING]

00:34.200 --> 00:37.504
I'm kidding. Want to spin? Yeah.

00:40.273 --> 00:42.709
- CASSIE: Yay!
- ASHLEY: Yay.

00:47.746 --> 00:48.780
BEN: Dad!

00:49.314 --> 00:55.054
MAN ON TV: <i>There's decay
feeding on fear, hate, death.</i>

00:56.588 --> 00:57.589
<i>Death is everywhere.</i>

00:59.091 --> 01:00.359
<i>No one is immune.</i>

01:02.195 --> 01:04.397
<i>I see the pain you've given me
as a gift.</i>

01:06.665 --> 01:07.733
<i>Once you give in...</i>

01:08.801 --> 01:11.271
<i>things become much easier.</i>

01:13.105 --> 01:14.506
DAVID ON RECORDING: <i>What else
has it told you?</i>

01:16.242 --> 01:17.477
<i>Look at me, Jacob.</i>

01:19.646 --> 01:21.114
<i>What else has it told you?</i>

01:22.382 --> 01:23.683
JACOB ON RECORDING:
<i>Pray for you doctor.</i>

01:25.150 --> 01:26.786
<i>Last night, the rake
spoke your name.</i>

01:29.287 --> 01:31.191
DAVID ON RECORDING:
<i>What is the rake, Jacob?</i>

01:31.590 --> 01:33.291
JACOB ON RECORDING: <i>It's too
hard to describe, doctor.</i>

01:34.427 --> 01:37.193
Murphy's entity draws
inspiration from that

01:37.195 --> 01:40.665
of the Native American Wendigo
and the ancient Celtic Arrach.

01:41.599 --> 01:45.502
This disease attaches itself
to willing or unwilling hosts

01:45.504 --> 01:49.142
and grows inside effectively,
leeching off of his or her life.

01:50.275 --> 01:52.844
Jacob believes he must appease
this entity by bringing harm

01:53.078 --> 01:55.647
to himself and infecting those
around him.

